# Cursor Blink Test
# Tests Set CursorBlink false to disable cursor blinking
Output examples/dvds/cursor-blink-test.svg

Set Width 800
Set Height 300
Set FontSize 16
Set Theme dracula
Set Title "Cursor Blink Disabled"
Set CursorBlink false
Set PromptPrefix "\x1b[95m❯\x1b[0m "

Type "Cursor should not blink"
Sleep 2s
